{
  "stem": "10162.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I decided all the time that whatever they give me, I will drink it and eat it because, that's what I would have to do for my mother.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember the sisters, who I mentioned-- that's why I mentioned them, because they wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would just-- they couldn't take it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They couldn't take a sip of this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's so bad, they couldn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they both died right there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were-- before-- they weren't put in a crematorium or anything, but they died, like so many others, because of weakness and starvation.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I ate everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't care what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I just-- everything I ate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And one very surreal thing I remember that was-- even in Auschwitz, it was surreal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "One day, they marched us out and we had to sit on this side of the road in like a yoga position.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I don't remember if we got for that day some kind of a clothes, different clothes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We would always get something different to wear.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had to go-- frequently, we went to the bath, you know, which was a disinfectant in this big room where there were holes in the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then we were told that-- well, we always had water coming out of there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But that was the same where the Zyklon gas came from.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And when we were finished, then they would throw us some kind of a clothes from whoever, whoever-- whatever they had.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--disinfected clothes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, what they took off, I guess, from the bodies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They disinfected everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Clean it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything was clean.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
